comments: I noticed that every word corresponded to a shape, but I couldn't figure out how to correctly guess the colour. Zapiko for example reminded me of spikes, and I linked it to the spiky shape. I didn't use any paper to take notes, I tried to do it all mentally. After learning the words and slowly accostuming myself to recognize the patterns, I had the most difficulty trying to guess if there was a pattern at all to the colours. In the end, I figured out that they might've been random, unless I missed a crucial detail.
